headline: Valero Energy says it will buy Venezuelan crude from three sellers
summary: By Nicole Jao and Vallari Srivastava Jan 29 (Reuters) - Valero Energy has engaged ​with three authorized sellers of ‌Venezuelan crude and will purchase barrels from all ‌three of them, it said on a conference call on Thursday. The refiner did not disclose the sellers, ⁠but added that ‌it expects Venezuelan crude will make up a "pretty large ‍part of its heavy crude diet" in February and March.
